## MSIX / packaging
AppPackages/
BundleArtifacts/
*.appx
*.appxbundle
*.appxupload
*.msix
*.msixbundle
*.msixupload
*.pfx
*.cer
# Allow the public signing cert checked in for CI to use during MSIX
# signing. Its private-key PFX half lives only in the SIGNING_PFX_BASE64
# GitHub Actions secret and must never be committed.
!scripts/signing/noteshard-signing.cer
# Local bootstrap output from scripts/bootstrap-signing-cert.ps1 — the
# base64-encoded PFX is a secret, paste it into SIGNING_PFX_BASE64 and
# delete it locally.
signing-pfx.b64
scripts/signing/*.pfx
GeneratedArtifacts/
# Dev-cert scratch area (see tools/New-DevCert.ps1). Lives under %LocalAppData%
# so is normally outside the tree, but guard explicitly in case a developer
# copies it in for any reason. Must never be committed.
**/dev-cert/

